---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Marie Poulin Case Study | Dino Favara Jr."
  description="Went from dabbling without a strategy to breaking out of '300 view jail,' averaging 2K views per video, and hitting a 300K+ view breakout."
>
  <Nav />

  <main>
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-10">
      <a href="/work" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary/70 hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">
        &larr; All case studies
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-8 pb-12">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-pink-500/10 text-pink-700 tracking-wide mb-6">
        Start From Zero
      </span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem)] leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-dark mb-4">
        Marie Poulin
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg font-light text-dark/60 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        Went from dabbling without a strategy to breaking out of "300 view jail," averaging 2K views per video, and hitting a 300K+ view breakout.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-6">
        {['Start From Zero Program', 'Content Coaching', 'Format Development', 'Short-Form Strategy'].map(tag => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-dark/10 bg-white/60 text-xs font-medium text-dark/55">{tag}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/70 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr]">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-3">Before</span>
            <span class="font-display text-[2.8rem] leading-none text-red-500">~300</span>
            <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-light text-dark/50">avg views per video (posting without a strategy)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center px-4"><span class="text-2xl text-dark/20">&rarr;</span></div>
          <div class="flex md:hidden items-center justify-center py-2"><span class="text-2xl text-dark/20">&darr;</span></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 px-8 text-center bg-pink-500/4">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-3">After</span>
            <span class="font-display text-[2.8rem] leading-none text-pink-600">300K+</span>
            <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-light text-dark/50">views on breakout video</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {[
          { value: '300K+', label: 'Breakout Video Views', sub: '' },
          { value: '22K', label: 'Views Within First 12 Videos', sub: '' },
          { value: '~2K', label: 'Avg Views Per Video', sub: '(from ~300)' },
          { value: 'Multiple', label: 'Videos Over 10K Views', sub: '' },
        ].map(m => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/60 p-5 text-center">
            <span class="font-display text-2xl text-pink-600">{m.value}</span>
            <p class="mt-1 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/45">{m.label}</p>
            {m.sub && <p class="mt-0.5 text-[10px] text-dark/35">{m.sub}</p>}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
      <article class="prose-custom">
        <h3>The Situation</h3>
        <p>Marie Poulin is an online business owner with a following in the Notion and productivity space. She had been dabbling with short-form video, posting occasionally without a clear strategy or system. But she wasn't seeing results. Her videos were stuck in "300 view jail" — the plateau where content gets seen by almost no one because the algorithm hasn't learned who to serve it to.</p>

        <h3>The Approach</h3>
        <p>Marie joined the Start From Zero program, which is designed to take everything I learned over 4+ years of obsessive short-form experimentation and condense it into an actionable system. The focus was on giving her a format library, hook structures, and a posting rhythm she could actually maintain. Not just theory, but a system that produces results from the first batch of videos.</p>

        <h3>The Results</h3>
        <p>Within her first 12 videos posted after working with me, Marie had a video hit 22K views and multiple videos crossing the 10K view mark. She broke out of the "300 view jail" that traps most new creators and raised her average views to approximately 2,000 per video — a 6-7x improvement over the typical new-account baseline.</p>
        <p>Towards the end of our time together, her content hit critical mass: a video broke out and generated over 300,000 views. The system had compounded. Format clarity, audience signal, and algorithmic trust all working together.</p>
      </article>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-dark/8">
        <span class="text-sm font-light text-dark/45">Timeline: Start From Zero program engagement</span>
        <div class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-full rounded-full bg-dark/6 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-full rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-400 to-periwinkle" style="width: 60%"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/60 p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="font-display text-xl text-dark">Want results like this?</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-light text-dark/55 mt-1">Let's talk about building your content engine.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="mailto:dino@mercurysocialmedia.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-primary text-off-white font-medium text-sm hover:bg-primary/90 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/40 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 active:scale-95 whitespace-nowrap">
          Email me &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-custom h3 { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--dark); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .prose-custom h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .prose-custom p { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(26, 21, 35, 0.65); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .prose-custom strong { font-weight: 500; color: var(--dark); }
  .prose-custom blockquote { border-left: 3px solid var(--primary); padding: 1rem 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; background: rgba(107, 92, 231, 0.04); border-radius: 0 0.75rem 0.75rem 0; }
  .prose-custom blockquote p { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .prose-custom blockquote cite { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(26, 21, 35, 0.45); }
</style>
